data.description: Fully Furnished and appliances!  Seller will pay 4,000$ towards Closing Costs at Close of Escrow!!  Beautiful home here in Yuma Amazing opportunity for First time home buyers and Investors that are looking for that all in one package. Its less than 5 min from variety of food and shopping of all kinds. Near accouple of Yuma's beautiful parks!  This house has solar panels as well for that great money saving electricity.
